title: It's Winter! Holiday Cards
description:
The artist of this design, Katherine Gaspar, says "My dream is that wherever I end up in life, I will be happy—with my friends, family, and the world.". These unique holiday cards were created by a student employed in the Marwen Foundation career development programs. Marwen is an after-school arts organization that provides high-quality visual arts, college planning, and career development programs--all free of charge--to Chicago's under-served young people.
  • Dimensions: Cards 5 x 7 in.
  • Materials: Box set of 12 cards w/envelopes
  • Inside Message: Blank
